raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "ODENet" %}
{% set version = "0.0.4" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }} 

source:
  url: https://github.com/uqyge/{{ name }}/archive/{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: d060a64004b12fbb61eff60618f8afd5c843f4dc4f5289b5df195269e69a23ab

build:
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv"
  noarch: python

requirements:
  host:
    - python
    - pip
  run:
    - python
    - tensorflow >=1.14
    - pandas
    - scikit-learn

test:
  imports:
    - ODENet

about:
  home: http://github.com/uqyge/ODENet
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: 'ODENet for combustion'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - uqyge
    - icehuli
    - mhansinger
